OL,3,CVan driver stabbed in suspected
OL,4,Cvehicle robbery
OL,6,FA man has suffered serous stab wounds
OL,7,Fin a suspected van robbery in
OL,8,FMaidstone.
OL,10,FIt is alleged the victim, who is in
OL,11,Fhis early 50s, was assaulted by two
OL,12,Fmen before his white Sprinter van was
OL,13,Fstolen.
OL,15,FHe was treated by South East Coast
OL,16,FAmbulance Service and taken to a
OL,17,FLondon hospital, where his condition
OL,18,Fis described as serious but stable.
OL,20,FThe attack happened in Reculver Walk
OL,21,Fat 7.44am on Saturday 18 July.
