OL,3,CVan driver stabbed in suspected
OL,4,Cvehicle robbery
OL,6,FPatrols completed a search of the area
OL,7,Fand the victim's van was located in
OL,8,FWoolley Road.
OL,10,FA knife was also recovered in Reculver
OL,11,FWalk.
OL,13,FA 45-year-old man was arrested by
OL,14,Farmed officers in Swanscombe and taken
OL,15,Finto custody.
